<!-- ============================================ 
  Síntesis de la lección (discusión de cierre)
=================================================  -->
<subsubsection xml:id="lec-analicemosAlgoritmosDeResta-sintesis" component="profesor">
  <shorttitle><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></shorttitle>
  <title><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></title>
  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>(10 mins)</title>

  <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
  <ul>
    <li><q>Hemos aprendido varios algoritmos de resta. ¿Cuál algoritmo de resta es su favorito y por qué?</q> (The expanded form algorithms because we can really see all the parts of the number. The algorithm where we decompose the units as we go because I don’t like to do them all at once. The algorithms that use 1 digit for each place value because they don’t take as long to write.)</li>
  </ul>

</subsubsection>



